ze-full wp-image-1099497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY6-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><h2><span style="color: #000000;">消費券搭車自動扣款</span></h2><p><span style="color: #000000;">如果要用消費券搭港鐵，只需要在同樣的「服務」頁面，按「政府消費券」，然後繼續開啟「消費券用於『港鐵乘車碼』自動扣款服務」選項，之後每次使用乘車碼入閘，都會自動扣去消費券的餘額。</span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY18-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;">如果是新用戶，在 「優惠專區」輸入優惠碼「MTR50」就可以額外獲得總值 $50 電子現金券用來搭港鐵！如果是現有用戶，只要做齊三個狂賞印任務，就可以換 $5 電子現金券搭港鐵，無論返工還是放假都可以善用消費券和 ＷeChat Pay HK 的優惠去不同目的地。</span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY10-1536x864.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="844" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11.jpg 1500w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/WECHATPAY11-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><h2><span style="color: #000000;">日行一善做公益</span></h2><p><span style="color: #000000;">WeChat Pay HK 以及騰訊基金會最近更發起「日行一善」慈善活動，所有用戶每日以 WeChat Pay HK 完成首筆消費（包括搭車）都可以得到一個公益印花，用戶可從 3 個慈善機構選擇其中一個項目捐贈印花，消費同時做善事，慳錢又有意義。</span></p><p><span style="color: #000000;"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/279895308_2807827839364083_4603975534209337275_n-768x768.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></span></p><p><strong>相關影片: </strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=314&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fvideos%2F1347987489031125%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=560&amp;t=0" width="560" height="314" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe><br />&nbsp;</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
